      <scopecontent id="aspace_bf973ba8e9f5c2e3411a6b5e6542e380">
         <head>Scope and Contents</head>
         <p>The records consist of banking and financial records kept by Anson Phelps Stokes, the treasurer of the Yale Grenfell Association, concerning the construction of the ketch "Yale", a two masted sailing ship.</p>  
