            <scopecontent id="aspace_9da8b4e28cb3f56e4a3a0405f9ec06fb">
               <head>Scope and Contents</head>
               <p>These are the financial records, kept by the Treasurer of the Yale Grenfell Association, Anson Phelps Stokes, on the building of the ketch "Yale." The papers came to the library from the Secretary's Office in 1928 and were transferred from Beinecke Rare Book Library to the Archives in April 1981.</p>
